message.body: Lol u eat out all the time?
I've been getting better but cooking for myself makes so much food... If I cook its usually just a piece of fish with veggies
U like seafood? Yeah I pretty much make every meal myself. I can even come home everyday for lunch. Eating out is just so expensive and there aren't enough healthy options
True... That's nice that you have the option to go home. I eat my lunch with the students but I get to hear all the gossip that way
How young are Ur kids??
There in high school but they either dropped out or failed out before so they're a little older 16-20
oh damn. Is this a discipline school?
It's an alternative accelerated school. We're allowed to restrain the students but I've only had to do it twice in 3 years to stop fights... The students
I have now are pretty good. They all have their issues though
Damn I could never do what u do
It's not bad i usually have alot of fun... Reading books all day and talking about them
You have a hard job how do you budget without any money?
You make lots and lots of cuts and provide bad service lol
How was your day today?
Long and uneventful lol finally back at the gym now you?
It was crazy we've been doing state testing the past week so it was hard getting them back on track
It's it awfully sweaty at the gym?
Nah they got ac goin hard. when is school done for u?
June 24th...but I only have 17 more days of teaching
So lucky. Got plans for Summer?
Maybe summer school, getting in shape, going to the beach/pool, and I have a trip to Seattle with friends from college, and it's my ten year high school reunion
So besides the beach house you have any other plans?
I'm tryna goto California. But no other trips. Goto some concerts and stuff tho
U doin anything this weekend for memorial day
My friend is having a BBQ and hopefully the pool at my parents apartment will be open... I love the summer
What are your plans?
None yet. My friend from out ta time might come for the weekend but I haven't confirmed yet. I was gonna ask if u had any free time if u wanted to get together
Oh thanks I'm free Friday and then I'm heading back to jersey Saturday
Cool I will try and solidify my plans tomorrow
Ok cool just let me know
We should make Cuban food
Ha I prefer to make a good first impression and that will be disastrous
Lol we would both be cooking! Lol how could it be that bad.
It we could hate each other and that would be awkward
Lol! Why would dinner make us hate each other? Haha this is funny
Well what if we don't like me and then you're stuck making a meal with me?
lol I'm sure I could stand your company for a meal. I've talked to u for a couple days now. I dun think Ur crazy or anything
we dun have to do that tho it was just an idea
Lol well I am crazy--crazy cool!!!!!
I think the idea is cool and different even though an out of control fire may result from it.... I would just prefer it at a second or third outing to en
Lol well that'd good
sure that you don't run away from the mere sight of me
Lol u sound like you've never made food before lol
Well Cuban food is complicated
Lol pineapples can't be that complicated. Haha jk I have no idea what Cuban food is
Ha yes well those babies are hard to grow!
I mean cut
So whose concert do you want to go see this summer?
Lol I must admit I've never cut a pineapple
I'm looking to go the atmosphere concert
Well see if anyone else I like comes to town
I've never heard of atmosphere what kind of music is that?
Like alternative rap. What kind of music do u like??
Is it rap with a message? I like to use rap songs when I teach poetry but some of it is so bad
I like wale, common, and immortal technique when I teach... I like Motown, 90's boy bands, r&b
I mean he's def not a gangsta rapper. White dude from Minneapolis
I'll have to play some for u
Yes I'm intrigued now
So what r u gonna do with the rest of Ur night
Just grading some papers now and then I'm going to watch criminal minds
Yeah I gotta find out what's going on in south Africa. I'm up to the 1500s. Dutch merchants are ruling the seas, Fuckin up the Portuguese and making mad money
What year does it go up to?
He usually writes to present day. Whatever time it is when he wrote the book or close to it
That's cool will Charlize Theron be in it she's from South Africa?
You'll be an expert on all things South Africa that must be one hefty book
Lol I doubt it. Maybe Mandela though. Yeah his books are thousands of pages. Usually takes me bout a month to finish
Must be hard to cuddle up in bed with that behemoth
Do you read any fiction?
Yeah I try to force myself too but sometimes its so dry. With Michener I get both. Historical fiction
Fiction? Dry? Oh my.... I need to read more non fiction but I always choose something else at the bookstore
Whoops I had fiction and non fiction backward lol
Yea I def read fiction lol
Thank goodness that was almost a deal breaker
Lol
Yea I love jhumpa lahiri and Amy tan. Ever read there stuff??
No I've heard of both authors though
What's your favorite book?
the namesake by jhumpa lahiri
You might like them. They write about characters that are usually descendants of multi cultural heritage and struggle to find their identity.
Because I am mixed it often resonates with me. Maybe it would with u too
I heard that book is very good
Yea i loved it
How's work?
Lol so boring. I have nothing to do
I'm just surfing the internet
What no wonder the district is in peril
Lol trust me thats not why
So looks like I'm free tomorrow
Oh yeah?
Yea do u wanna hang out?
Yea what did you have in mind and when
7 is good for me..ummm I guess making Cuban food is out. We can play board games at my house or we could go to some bars in Fairmount. Or we could make a different meal
U have any other thoughts?
I think it's supposed to rain so anything outside will be out
What type of games do you have?
Taboo cards scrabble. Maybe we could go get one
Maybe we can go to a bar first in worried your not gonna like me
Maybe we can go to a bar first in worried your not gonna like me
And then if we're having fun we can okay a game
Y do u say that?
Because I never updated my pictures and I feel like I look different now
Look the same to me lol
But that sounds good to me for tomorrow
Is 7 good for u??9
7 is perfect
Lol well just promise not to run away
Lol u had a bad experience or something?
Ha no I am just super awkward
lol why, r u shy?
Yes at first .... I still get anxious teaching some days even though I love it and can hide it well
Well there's nothing to be shy about. We gonna have a good time!
Lol ok I'm looking forward to it
Yes I can't wait for this work week to be over
Yes must be draining surfing the web ;)
There's only so many articles to read online lol...
You have to get some evils
I meant e books
Nah can't be all blatant with it lol
I sit right next to CFO and budget director too it sux
Do you finish your work quickly or it's not your busy period right now?
That stinks I'm in a trailer outside so all I see is the students administration rarely harasses me
Your in a trailer outside? Summer is slow
I got free tix to a play tonight. Wanna go??
Venus in fur
Yea sure what time is it?
Suzanne Roberts theater
This rain def not making me wanna brave the elements tho
I know it's so cold and windy
So did you still want to go?
What do u think. I'm up for just goin out to the bar or goin to the show
The show sounds cool
Should I meet you there?
If u want or we can meet at my place and take subway down
U wanna go out and get a few drinks beforehand?
I can pick you up unless you think parking will be bad
Drinks sound good too
Yea I just think its easier to not drive. We could even take cab its not far
Ok
What time should I meet you at the bar?
Just meet up at my house is best. Then we can take a cab downtown
Ok what time and where is it?
Should we dress up??
Well I was planning on wearing jeans and heels
Yea I guess its just a play. I have no in between shoes lol just sneakers and dress shoes
Where nothing
Wear
I dun think that'll fly lol
Aww shucks
Way too cold out for that
Indeed....
Hey I'm probably going to be there closer to 6:30
k
Hey sorry had to find a spot I'm in front of your house now
Dun c u
Thanks for everything I enjoyed the play and your company. It was nice to meet you and I look forward to seeing you again... If you could just remember m
y name ;).... N pire 4 life
Ha now you do but last night you didn't... It doesn't matter though I still had fun
Alcohol is crazy
Ha yes it can be but it gets an unfair rep
lol what do u mean?
Well poor alcohol everything gets blamed on it... Fights, bad judgement, illness. When will it be its time to shine?
Lol college
Well that's true
U in jerz?
Yes got here a little while ago just hanging with the cam
Fam
What are you up to this weekend? Attending any bbqs?
Nah prolly not. I got invited to a party tomorrow but I dunno if I wanna go
Do you not know the person well?
Nah I do just not all that close. I should probably start working on some new video stuff too
How long u stayin in Jersey
My friends are having a BBQ tomorrow so ill be back in philly Sunday night or Monday morning
You are going to shoot a video or do you have film you need to edit?
I wanna practice some new software stuff.
I bought some things I haven't even looked at yet
That's cool... What does the software do?
I dun really k ow yet. Its just some plugins to make shit look cool lol
As cool as you?....impossible
Ha we'll see
